text: Oussama Tebbi (; born September 23, 1991) is an Algerian footballer who plays for AS Aïn M'lila in the Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1. == MC Alger == On July 2019, he signed a contract with ES Setif on a free transfer. == References == ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1991 births Category:Algerian footballers Category:RC Relizane players Category:MC Alger players Category:ES Sétif players Category:Association football forwards
